    </p>
    
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Joining AWS marked a pivotal moment in my career. Here, I've had the opportunity to work with cutting-edge cloud technologies, help build the Migration Acceleration Program (MAP), and contribute to the Well-Architected Framework that guides millions of customers worldwide.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
